	<Title>
		Fitness tip: Include your friends
	</Title>
	<Body>
		&lt;p&gt;Exercise doesn&apos;t have to be drudgery. And you don&apos;t need to go it alone. Sign up for a group exercise class or join a softball, soccer or volleyball team. Work out with a friend at a health club or gym. Start a walking group with friends and neighbors.&lt;/p&gt;
